				<wikidot:authorName>wishun</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1204404</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Couldn't he just show them?</p> <p>-Jimmy, come here! Ya gotta see this!<br /> -*sigh* What is it this time, Russell? Found more CIA implants in your teeth?<br /> -There's little men in the TV! And they run around and make the picture!<br /> -Of course there are. And I'm sure they wear little suits for the different colors.<br /> -No! They're all naked and their skin is green or red and what not.<br /> -&#8230;.Dammit, Russell! You can't just stop taking your meds like this!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
